GLOBAL THREAT INTELLIGENCE HUB:
The optional Global Threat Intelligence sharing feature transmits only
anonymized, hashed data (SHA-256 email hashes, IP addresses, boolean flags).
No personally identifiable information (names, raw emails, phone numbers,
billing addresses) is ever transmitted. Participation is opt-in only and
can be revoked at any time with full data erasure per GDPR Article 17.

DATA PROCESSING:
